de.feu.showgo.model

Class ParseElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.feu.showgo.model.ParseElement

  • public class ParseElement
extends java.lang.Object
    An element in a parsed dom tree. It contains a tag name, a text and a list of children which is empty for leafs.
